  m_Name: Dialogue Day 1 Encounter 5
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueHidesSubmit: 0
  lines:
  - "Oh.. You\u2019re the father of Romina, are you not? "
  - "I\u2019ve just come from the orphanage myself, I\u2019ve been working as her
    mentor, and oh if she hasn\u2019t been just the best!"
  - Such a kind, gentle soul, she gets along amazingly with all the kids, and makes
    them just as happy as she is.
  - You must have raised her so well, we all appreciate her efforts so much.
  - "You: That\u2019s\u2026. amazing to hear, thank you so much."
